[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あっ！　あそこの船２隻！　変てこ仮面さんが\n言ってたのはきっとアレですよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00204",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "確かにこの辺りじゃ見たことのない船……\n怪しいです！！　もう一度言います、怪しいです！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00205",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "片方は見たことがある。\nノーヴァ神聖国の船に見られる特徴だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00206",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、そうなんですか……って、もしかしてボス\n１０００以上ある島の船の特徴を全部覚えて……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00207",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "当然のことだ。お前も覚えろ、タイニー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00208",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "う……はい。でも、そんなボスでも\nもう片方の船は知らないってことですよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00209",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ということは、諸島同盟の外から来た船って\nことなんでしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00210",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "何かありそうだな。いくぞ、警戒しておけよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00211",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "諸島同盟監察官、エルス・マーティンだ。\n貴船の入国審査を執り行う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00212",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あっ、エルスさん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00213",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "お前は……アルビーナ・ジムロックか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00214",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボス、お知り合いですか？　　あっ、こういう場合、\n知り合いですか、でいいんですっけ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00215",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "神聖国の監査をした時に\n何度か顔を合わせたことがある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00216",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "だが案内人であるお前がなぜ他国に？\nこの船は観光船ということか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00217",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まあ、半分観光みたいなものですわ……\n乗ってるのは大陸から来た人たちでして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00218",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "よろしくお願いします！　\nレスナ・シュテルネンリヒトです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00219",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ラ、ラン、ランララ、ランターナ大陸から！？\n航路が確立されたという話は聞いてましたが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00220",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "こ、こちらこそよろしくお願いしますです！\nブラオールへ、ようこそ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00221",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー。まだ審査も終わっていないのに\n勝手に歓迎するんじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00222",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "す、すみません～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00223",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "な、なんだか随分初々しい監察官さんっすね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00224",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "しょ、精進中ですぅ～……懸命にぃ～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00225",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "さあタイニー、仕事だ。\n入国審査をアルビーナに対してやってみろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00226",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "アルビちゃんで、お仕事に慣れるといいっすよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00227",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "こういう性格の人間だ。場数を踏ませてもらえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00228",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "えっと、ではアルビーナさん。\nブラオールへの入国目的を教えてください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00229",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ブラオールからケイウンに寄贈された\n「九偉人図」と呼ばれる絵画を調べにきたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00230",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ええと……観光ではないんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00231",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "神聖国の事情みたいなものです。詳しくは\n話せないんですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00232",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "どうやら訳アリのようだな。\n長くなっても構わん、審査を続けろタイニー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00233",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "疲れた……さすがブラオール。入国審査大変なのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00234",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でもですね、ボスのお説教なんてもっと長くて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00235",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00236",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ひっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00237",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ひとまず、目的は承知した。諸島同盟の秩序を\n乱すものではないようだ。入国を許可しよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00238",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ただ「九偉人図」なる絵画は生憎聞き覚えがない。\n我々は島同士の取引も監視しているのだが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00239",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "本部に戻れば資料がありますかね～？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00240",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ああ。他の監察官の管轄なのだろう。\n資料室を当たってみて、何か分かり次第連絡しよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00241",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ありがとうございます。\nお二人の力、頼りにしてます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00242",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "では、今度こそ……改めまして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00243",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "諸島同盟中心地、ブラオールへ、ようこそ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00244",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]